'''Lorrad Flightworks''' was a company that manufactured [[Repulsorcraft/Legends|repulsorcraft]]. Their most notable product was the [[H-12 copter]] [[Airspeeder/Legends|airspeeder]], which was used by the well-off citizens of [[Desevro/Legends|Desevro]] living within the [[City/Legends|city]] of [[Maslovar]].

